<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8382695>
    dc:description "Figs 106–115. Morphology of the male genitalia for species of the subgenus Alpigenobombus Skorikov, 1914, from the dorsal aspect, anterior at the bottom of the image, posterior at the top. 106. Bombus wurflenii Radoszkowski, 1860, Turkey. 107. B mastrucatus Gerstaecker, 1869, Austria. 108. B. kashmirensis Friese, 1909, India-Kashmir. 109. B. rainai Williams, 2022, India-Kashmir. 110. B. sikkimi Friese, 1918, Nepal. 111. B. nobilis Friese, 1905, China-Sichuan. 112. B. validus Friese, 1905, China-Gansu. 113. B. genalis Friese, 1918, China-Yunnan. 114. B. breviceps Smith, 1852, China- Sichuan. 115. B. grahami (Frison, 1933) China-Sichuan (left penis-valve recurved hook missing). Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8382695/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

